The '''bastaska''' was a [[Crystal/Legends|crystal]] [[Spear/Legends|spear]] that the [[Gutretee (species)|Gutretee]] used.

==Description==
The bastaska could be transformed into a three [[Meter/Legends|meter]] [[Crystal/Legends|crystal]] rope, which was used during the ritual that the Gutretees performed whenever they encountered a new "tribe."<ref name="IC">''[[The Isis Coordinates]]''</ref>

